Package: VanillaCalendar
Title: Interactive Calendar Widget for R and Shiny
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Xavier", "EscribÃ  Montagut", email = "xavier.escriba.montagut@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R interface to the Vanilla Calendar Pro JavaScript library for creating
    interactive and customizable calendar widgets. The package enables integration
    of modern calendar components in R and Shiny applications with support for various
    display options and event handling capabilities.
